  <num>42-3404.36</num>
  <heading proof="needed">Assignment of District rights.</heading>
  <text>The Mayor may assign the opportunity to purchase provided under <cite path="42|34|IV">subchapter IV of this chapter</cite> to a qualified purchaser certified pursuant to <cite path="§42-3404.02d">§ 42-3404.02d</cite> that agrees to obligate itself and any successors in interest to maintain the affordability required by <cite path="§42-3404.33">§ 42-3404.33</cite>.</text>
